-- Gold Held in Exchange-Traded Funds Advances to Record 2,113.2 Metric Tons
-- B y   C h a n y a p o r n   C h a n j a r o e n
-- 2010-12-20T00:45:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-20/gold-held-in-exchange-traded-funds-advances-to-record-2-113-2-metric-tons.html
Gold assets held in exchange-traded
products rose 0.7 percent from a day earlier to a  record 2,113.2
metric tons  as of Dec. 17, according to data collected by
Bloomberg from 10 providers. Holdings have climbed 17.6 percent
this year.  To contact the reporter on this story:
